@jennycolgan A most poignant, beautiful tribute to not just those needing care, but their carers too. 

Yes we might have “underlying health issues” but despite what Dominic Cummings says our lives aren’t disposable.  Thanks to Rory Kinnear in this tribute to Karina speaks for many. #COVID19
